# options for the grit tool. (sprites)
#
# (-gt) gen tiles
# (-gT) set transparent color rrggbb hexadecimal
# (-gB) set bit depth
# (-m)  include map data (or not) (doesn't by default)
# (-mLs) tile map layout (using reg sbb option)
# (-mR) tile reductions: t = tiles, p = palette, f = flipped
# (-p)  include palette data
# (-ft) export as binary data [*.bin]
# (-fh) toggle header file generation

-gt -gB4 -gu16 -m -mLs -mRtpf -mu16 -p -ftb -fh!